Interface ISalesForceResponse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IUMPResponse, java.io.Serializable

    public interface ISalesForceResponse
extends IUMPResponse
    The interface ISalesForceResponse provides an abstraction to retrieve the result from executing a SalesForce.com web service
